{"tid":34581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，依家啲人究竟係風趣定賤格？","createTime":"2016-12-11T14:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T06:07:55.000Z","uid":5190,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64de67242d67c0dfe8523a6b51b84b587eac4545","tid":34581,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"今日約左兩個fd去飲酒吹水<br />\n大家都隔好耐無見 咁緊係想吹多兩句啦<br />\n點知其中一個竟然帶堆條女黎 真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想放鬆去講男人野都唔得 要就住就住<br />\n咁好啦 四個人坐埋一齊吹下水睇下波咁<br />\n點知佢條女無啦啦撩我講野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂 你同我男朋友識左幾耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多有十年啦 做咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知唔知呢 依個世界有兩種人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊兩種人？<br />\n之後佢就攬住條仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一種就係好人 同我仔仔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁另一種呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另一種係樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係依一刻我以為佢諗住話鳩我係第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁即係點？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪中間個種人囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁即係點？<br />\n原來我唔係樣衰個種人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係好樣衰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我一手掉撚左個杯落地下 再屌鳩係話 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞港女</span></span> 然後就走左<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母恰鳩我毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc981e72dff3fb01aa43d125a1d2f3db75cab0b","tid":34581,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5d684700b35117c020f32488e589a16ced7a6f","tid":34581,"uid":4559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2351d960cdf934602eab946d40ff5e6847fdbe75","tid":34581,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56e567a3cd40267a6bbf68ffaa8419e094ef3e5","tid":34581,"uid":49049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家好少女仔咁老實架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n忍唔到笑sor"},{"pid":"31c286f711e7aed815e04dcd4b7ac1b9f55e9919","tid":34581,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"舊故包裝下又可以當新故<br />\n<br />\nbtw正皮左"},{"pid":"c7758b5784ad6007d43fdd4fa5c666ff0bca2962","tid":34581,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你肯定係十二少"},{"pid":"8c4f6ee8806ddf866d67f288a51e3bc2773d214a","tid":34581,"uid":20248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"網上<br />\